tags.description: In 2004, Pisgah’s ball field was named one of the Top 10 Vintage Baseball Diamonds in the state of Iowa by the Society of American Baseball Research.  This was the home field of Bob Wiltse and Loren Babe.
tags.name: Vintage Baseball Diamond
